957b83276002b0e8e465179710121cc706e6a","tid":1788340,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:18:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WISHING YOU A HOLIDAY SEASON FULL OF WARMTH, LOVE AND FAMILY <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"363b8a18a271a2e1a002caf30de1970fd8d5a258","tid":1788340,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T15:58:03.000Z","msg":"May the beauty of the holidays warm up spirit !"},{"pid":"c11a96c8c2a8abc8222ba144497b8c22bfe86177","tid":1788340,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"Season's greetings! Wishing you a new year full of peace and joy!"},{"pid":"be9e60f2455df9e97e108ad0f3275e204193c60a","tid":1788340,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"Yuletide greetings"},{"pid":"a5718dea9e7adea71c011f7a682fd52b5d836fea","tid":1788340,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:32:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">Happy holidays <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"40ebf3ebbd065ea5babf261c71142237c48436c2","tid":1788340,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子在大自然的階級觀念</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n在大自然內，兔子有等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔子會groom (舔/梳理) 一個次級(inferior)兔子，但高級的亦會要求次級的兔子groom牠。當兔子低頭向前躺在地上，牠是想你groom (撫摸/親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、安全感、令牠舒適快樂。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令到冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。兔子會騎着另一隻兔背後來顯示牠是較高層次(show dominance), 此行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度。此行為是正常，無論兩隻是同性或異性。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">在0:59 可看到：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=546744de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你在兔子面前<span style=\"color: gold;\">打開手掌</span>，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果你們關係好，牠會做。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">主人要求兔仔groom 主人：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=1685f4f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a><br />\n<br />\n以下兩隻兔子決定等級制度時<span style=\"color: gold;\">遇到困難</span>。一隻 groom另一隻, 但等了很久還未得到回報，所以發脾氣在<strong><em>2:08</em></strong>咬牠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=7d2fce6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a><br />\n<br />\n除了騎着兔子背後，兔子還會躺在另一隻兔的頸上來顯示牠是較高層次(show dominance), 此行為停了就代表已決定了等級制度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9WUGogDlg4&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=d9940221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">資訊來源:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=65eace99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>&nbsp;(頭3個chapters)</span>"},{"pid":"f539eac6b2db4524b7bb4d21dd748b9d7d19e587","tid":1788340,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7c4948ac65371782e9f4795f733cd29eebfb79","tid":1788340,"uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbc4eda28f405155b36dbcfaba71a1f2b0b9d02","tid":1788340,"uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3a5d1136d46bcd2